  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "g stack hit eighty-nine thousand stars in a few weeks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:26d308d3c0fed3ee174e76ec29d8c87f3e77ee5d88ef625a0e0c6e9b3bd1d480",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "So \u2014 what is it? And do you need it? Garry Tan, the CEO of Y Combinator, open-sourced it earlier this year.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fb1f4d660f13d0d3e6b0f0c949ce29fc1b76f2f9c0c4ac6b6cf10a9160bb6a24",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 7.383945578231293,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Today it has eighty-nine thousand GitHub stars and over three hundred pull requests.",
      "checksum": "sha256:56f254f2c3e4e1066b11fa7a9bdf38121713e9e8cae14b20add423e890fa88af",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 32
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "At its core, g stack is a pack of slash-commands for Claude Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:23840b77d2d7171bc7472589bfa26c4037340a4330d411b55de6ecdce4f105ae",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 45
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Specialist roles instead of a blank prompt.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d180ce9a3b5835836eeea55266001cec89552afef3440ab9e7698db3409d73de",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 58
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "All markdown. All free. Twenty-three specialist skills.",
      "checksum": "sha256:16aaa760a7ebe1506152e9036c6ad88b30c02436377fb2de57dbe68f1c2c513b",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 65
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Eight power tools. Twenty-eight commands in total \u2014 covering planning, design, code review, browser testing, and shipping the pull-request.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eeb7c36473d68c78218df7d1fb566c5da852c5b55e4aebab2018423f439bd444",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 7.848344671201814,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "The most-talked-about skill is office-hours.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bdeb472d181a868515b1e0ff7090a1617339e5b22487c53ff68e469cbbd9dca9",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 91
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "It asks six forcing questions about your product before you ship a single line of code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:07d9104d84ddd8e30bbb121daff17cb72e1de9bdc9518181cf617c935c2b3533",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 96
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "So \u2014 does it work? Some founders say yes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:af716ea68d761cac5e78f95b00f47085546c0c24760ae7f45a57324d79693ede",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 112
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "They report shipping faster, getting un-stuck on architecture, and using office-hours to invalidate ideas before they waste a weekend on them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3a2efadd8bd75375af9dda91861f3b8b51c6591496ebc2618689838105f846db",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 7.9412244897959186,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 121
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "The praise is real. Others are skeptical.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c6298e0d47ac75f7d1a4b8c353e937cb99249e4574e8a117015c943a1e5b1f12",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 142
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "They ask: is this really new \u2014 or is it Claude Code's existing plan and review commands wrapped up with nicer ergonomics?",
      "checksum": "sha256:aa762f72ea8babb116a2d9cdcaddfb3dbf6292e1329c0a853f5d6411bb963ce2",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 7.894784580498866,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 149
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "How is it different from BMAD or Spec Kit?",
      "checksum": "sha256:7a400f4225b25ef53d7583898115b0a9f74ef1d2347c85d0c2b6c57d9cf60b91",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 171
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "And critics push back further. At the end of the day, they say \u2014 these are markdown files.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e05a439489ef39ce729d1697173204a0b81998f19ae7aaecfa95c1c7ae35183f",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 5.433469387755102,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 180
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Stars on a repo aren't the same as production value.",
      "checksum": "sha256:345e836a8c3868d63a826e47dbea77b2ab127419a156a39afd9062a7d6eb02fb",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 198
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "So \u2014 we're not telling you what to think.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f8891ff93ab127df813a94c0b5824cd4959fa210d590c3b1925f350847c2ab46",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 208
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "We're asking. Have you tried g stack? What are you using to ship faster \u2014 g stack, BMAD, Spec Kit, superpowers, or just raw Claude Code?",
      "checksum": "sha256:c23ec1630b9f8a90be70522f6d555d543db372d938bbab20aefcbae08d0cbd10",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 9.102222222222222,
      "word_count": 26,
      "words_offset": 217
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Drop it in the comments. If you're working on this stuff seriously, come discuss it with builders inside Dynamous \u2014 link below.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9936fe9c26307404a7efe27066945f3a308a3d33ce01f634b7e0e08d1b9d167a",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 7.1053061224489795,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 243
    }
  ]
}